{"type": "article", "id": 8436, "title": "Boomerang 椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-14T07:46:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234917ksOzL0JPf1hyTlYS.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAnna Szonyi 为迪拜设计区设计了这款叫做 Boomerang 的椅子，他的灵感来源是时间的流逝。椅子的椅背和椅面可以绕着中轴自由旋转，从而在长椅之间营造出“隔间”，空间在一张椅子上不断变幻。此外，实木片的数量也可以更改，从而改变椅子的长度。Anna Szonyi 的这个作品获得了迪拜都市委员会设计奖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234913gph8DJOqU6BbwjNt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.57314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234914yNPJFvxVsu3gElTR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234914eM5KA1Sb6BL2qDVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234915DzYabqZWURSJOu29.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.62777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234915BogTqd9PwIl3v8bU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234916Ls2cnUlkjvoy1MpK.jpg\" alt=